Cooking brings about visions of beautiful food, engaging experiences with friends, healthy lifestyle, and creative endeavors.

18.description:
Cooking brings about visions of beautiful food, engaging experiences with friends, healthy lifestyle, and creative endeavors.

Cook books are on the shelves or in the kitchens of most homes, and recipes made a transition to the digital realm long ago, making recipe sites very popular online. In the newly burgeoning mobile and tablet space, recipe apps have also become popular.

Unfortunately, Cook books, online recipes, and many recipe apps fail to create an engaging experience which actually aids in the process of cooking! Do these tools make us better cooks and help us make better meals?

Kitchon is starting from scratch, recreating how we interact with recipes, how we discover what to cook, all with the goal of helping home cooks make better meals.

Kitchon is just past the prototype stage now, and some close friends are testing out the capabilities.

12.short_description: Cupónica is a online coupons company which offers attractive daily deals with huge discounts for local consumers.

18.description:
Cupónica is the main online coupons company developed in Argentina which offers attractive daily deals with huge discounts for local consumers. The proposals on carefully selected experiences, services and products enable Cupónica to connect medium-size businesses and merchants with local buyers.

How does it work? Taking advantage of Social Media, e-commerce and the daily newsletter sent to subscribed users, Cupónica drives audience to its web site driving online customers to offline businesses. It's simple, every day different proposals are presented for a city. After the purchase, buyers receive a coupon valid for exchanging the service/product at the store. This way, everyone wins: the consumer gets a big discount and the medium-size companies expand their business by increasing their sales and by reaching thousands of probable clients.

Cupónica encourages everyone to discover places, products and services in their towns at incredible prices. The company is constantly searching for the best offers for its clients to exploit all tempting proposals. In addition, Cupónica developed identifying features such as Cupónica Extras! which are other tempting discounts that complement the daily deal and can be redeemed by users at the stores as well. Buying is much simpler now: with Cupónica you don't need to wait for others to buy the product in order to activate your purchase, it will only depend on you.

Cupónica is a perfect complement to the integral solution that Fnbox properties provide to users by turning their lives more productive and enjoyable, while helping them to solve everyday problems. Since the beginning Fnbox is committed to provide the most reliable services such as linking users' needs to solutions with Cupónica, and achieving total customer satisfaction.

12.short_description: Studiosnaps rethinks the traditional photobooth concept to transform a most commonly considered party favor into a new form of outdoor

18.description:
Studiosnaps rethinks the traditional photobooth concept to transform a most commonly considered party favor into a new form of outdoor media. We develop software and electronics to make each booth an intelligent and real-time reactive brand utility that is both offline and online.
We are building this media by permanently placing photo booths in high traffic and exclusive locations. The photos are free to the consumer and we sell the ad-space on the photo, the screen, and the online integration to the brand.
With over three years of experience, we have seen the power that a free photo can have over a consumer.
Photobooths as a form of outdoor media have the ability to: 
-	Invite consumers to the brand 
-	Engage consumers and give them something to do while passively and actively mining information from them 
-	Generate real-time discount offers based on demographics, socio-economics, & interests. 
-	Track those offers & correlate the purchase with demographic & psychographic data.
